Place the mint sprigs and tea bags into a large pitcher. Pour boiling water over them, and allow to steep for about 8 minutes. Remove and discard the tea bags and mint leaves, squeezing out excess liquid. Stir in SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener until dissolved, then stir in the orange and lemon juices. Pour in the cold water. Serve over ice cubes, and garnish with orange and lemon slices.